      • createSinglePathParam

        public static <Id> IdSerializer<Id> createSinglePathParam(String name,
                                                          java.util.function.Function<String,Id> deserialize,
                                                          java.util.function.Function<Id,String> serialize)
        Create an IdSerializer from the given serialize and deserialize functions. This is useful for situations where the ID is expressed as a single parameter, and the name of that parameter doesn't matter.
        Type Parameters:
        Id - The type of the Id that this serializer is for.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the serializer. This is used for debugging purposes, so that the toString method returns something meaningful.
        deserialize - The deserialize function.
        serialize - The serialize function.
        Returns:
        The serializer.
        See Also:
        IdSerializer
